d Fox (footballer)|David Fox]]\n|{{flagicon|BEL}} [[Royal Antwerp F.C.|Royal Antwerp]]\n|-\n|29 July 2003\n|30 June 2004\n|MF\n|{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Michael Stewart (footballer)|Michael Stewart]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Nottingham Forest F.C.|Nottingham Forest]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Stewart wanders into Forest |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/3106723.stm |work=BBC Sport |date=29 July 2003 |accessdate=8 February 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n|24 August 2003\n|30 June 2004\n|GK\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ricardo (footballer, born 1971)|Ricardo]]\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Racing de Santander|Racing Santander]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Man Utd agree Ricardo loan |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_utd/3178051.stm |work=BBC Sport |date=24 August 2003 |accessdate=8 February 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n|12 September 2003\n|12 October 2003\n|FW\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Neil Wood]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Peterborough United F.C.|Peterborough United]]\n|-\n|19 September 2003\n|18 October 2003\n|GK\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ben Williams (footballer, born 1982)|Ben Williams]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Altrincham F.C.|Altrincham]]\n|-\n|24 October 2003\n|24 November 2003\n|FW\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Daniel Nardiello]]\n|{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Swansea City A.F.C.|Swansea City]]\n|-\n|24 October 2003\n|29 December 2003\n|DF\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Alan Tate (footballer)|Alan Tate]]\n|{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Swansea City A.F.C.|Swansea City]]\n|-\n|24 November 2003\n|25 December 2003\n|FW\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Danny Byrne]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Hartlepool United F.C.|Hartlepool United]]\n|-\n|2 January 2004\n|26 April 2004\n|GK\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Fabien Barthez]]\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Olympique de Marseille|Marseille]]\n|-\n|12 January 2004\n|16 December 2006\n|FW\n|{{flagicon|CHN}} [[Dong Fangzhuo]]\n|{{flagicon|BEL}} [[Royal Antwerp F.C.|Royal Antwerp]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Man Utd gain work permit for Dong |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_utd/6184803.stm |work=BBC 