lo-at-no-1-20151107|title=ARIA Singles: Adele Earns Platinum Status with 'Hello' at No 1|publisher=Noise11|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=November 7, 2015|access-date=November 7, 2015}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Denmark|title=Trap Queen|artist=Fetty Wap|type=single|award=Platinum|relyear=2014|relmonth=12|certyear=2015|recent=false|id=35|access-date=September 5, 2015}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Germany|artist=Fetty Wap|title=Trap Queen|award=Gold|relyear=2014|relmonth=04|certyear=2018|type=single|access-date=April 14, 2018}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Italy|artist=Fetty Wap|title=Trap Queen|award=Platinum|certyear=2017|type=single|salesamount=50,000}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=New Zealand|title=Trap Queen|artist=Fetty Wap|type=single|award=Platinum|relyear=2014|certyear=2015|recent=website|id=4145|access-date=September 19, 2015}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|title=Trap Queen|artist=Fetty Wap|type=single|award=Platinum|number=2|relyear=2015|certyear=2018|access-date=July 30, 2018}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|artist=Fetty Wap|title=Trap Queen|award=Diamond|relyear=2014|certyear=2019|type=single|access-date=April 22, 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|streaming=true}}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n!Date\n!Format\n!Version\n!Label(s)\n|-\n|April 22, 2014<ref name=orig_release/>\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[Music download|Digital download]]\n|Original version\n|Goodfella4life\n|-\n|December 15, 2014<ref name=re-release/>\n|Revised version\n|rowspan=\"3\"|{{hlist|RGF|[[300 Entertainment|300]]}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|May 4, 2015<ref name=remix/><ref name=azealia_remix/>\n|Remix<br />{{small|(featuring [[Quavo]] and [[Gucci Mane]])}}\n|-\n|Remix<br />{{small|(featuring [[Azealia Banks]], Quavo and Gucci Mane)}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n{{Fetty Wap}}\n\n[[Category:2014 songs]]\n[[Category:2014 debut singles]]\n[[Category:Billboard H