{"title_page": "Trimeresurus salazar", "text_new": "{{Speciesbox\n| image = Trimeresurus_salazar.jpg\n| taxon = Trimeresurus salazar\n| authority = Mirza et al., 2020\n}}\n\n'''''Trimeresurus salazar''''', also known as Salazar's pit viper, is a species of green [[pit viper]] discovered in the lowlands of the western part of [[Arunachal Pradesh]], India.<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Mirza|first=Zeeshan A.|last2=Bhosale|first2=Harshal S.|last3=Phansalkar|first3=Pushkar U.|last4=Sawant|first4=Mandar|last5=Gowande|first5=Gaurang G.|last6=Patel|first6=Harshil|date=2020-04-15|title=A new species of green pit vipers of the genus ''Trimeresurus'' Lac\u00e9p\u00e8de, 1804 (Reptilia, Serpentes, Viperidae) from western Arunachal Pradesh, India|url=https://zse.pensoft.net/article/48431/|journal=Zoosystematics and Evolution|language=en|volume=96(1)|pages=123\u2013138|doi=10.3897/zse.96.48431|issn=1860-0743}}</ref>\n\nIt was named after [[Salazar Slytherin]] from the ''[[Harry Potter]]'' series.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/04/21/world/salazar-slytherin-pit-viper-trnd/index.html |title=Scientists discover a new snake and name it after Salazar Slytherin |date=April 22, 2020| first=Leah|last= Asmelash|publisher=CNN}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{taxonbar|from=Q90903062}}\n{{Snake-stub}}\n[[Category:Trimeresurus|Salazar]]\n[[Category:Harry Potter]]\n", "text_old": "{{Speciesbox\n| image = Trimeresurus_salazar.jpg\n| taxon = Trimeresurus salazar\n}}\n\n'''''Trimeresurus salazar''''', also known as Salazar's pit viper, is a species of green [[pit viper]] discovered in the lowlands of the western part of [[Arunachal Pradesh]], India.<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Mirza|first=Zeeshan A.|last2=Bhosale|first2=Harshal S.|last3=Phansalkar|first3=Pushkar U.|last4=Sawant|first4=Mandar|last5=Gowande|first5=Gaurang G.|last6=Patel|first6=Harshil|date=2020-04-15|title=A new species of green pit vipers of the genus ''Trimeresurus'' Lac\u00e9p\u00e8de, 1804 (Reptilia, Serpentes, Viperidae) from western Arunachal Pradesh, India|url=https://zse.pensoft.net/article/48431/|journal=Zoosystematics and Evolution|language=en|volume=96(1)|pages=123\u2013138|doi=10.3897/zse.96.48431|issn=1860-0743}}</ref>\n\nIt was named after [[Salazar Slytherin]] from the ''[[Harry Potter]]'' series.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/04/21/world/salazar-slytherin-pit-viper-trnd/index.html |title=Scientists discover a new snake and name it after Salazar Slytherin |date=April 22, 2020| first=Leah|last= Asmelash|publisher=CNN}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{taxonbar|from=Q90903062}}\n{{Snake-stub}}\n[[Category:Trimeresurus|Salazar]]\n[[Category:Harry Potter]]\n", "name_user": "Dyanega", "label": "safe", "comment": "add authority", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trimeresurus_salazar"}
